notes: A few graphical glitches, such as sprites always showing on top of 3D objects even if you're standing behind them. Some textures showing up in wrong spots, or on top of things they shouldn't be on. Sometimes a few mode switches (for example from windowed to fullscreen and back) fixes these problems, sometimes not. If it starts behaving, it seems to stay that way for the remainder of your play session. Display output is slightly off-center in the window when playing in windowed mode.
